FLEEGER v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND HOUSE OF CORRECTION [App. No. 95,

September Term, 1964.]

Decided February 12, 1965.

Before Prescott, C. J., and Hammond, Marbury, Sybert and Barnes, JJ.

*643Per Curiam.

For the reasons stated in the opinion of Judge Rasin below, the application for leave to appeal is hereby denied.

Application denied.
